    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) featuring the legendary F22C1 power unit. This longitudinal 2.2L inline-four utilizes VTEC variable valve timing to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is mechanically sound, paired with a short-throw 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential for precise torque biasing during corner exit. The chassis maintains its structural integrity via the high-rigidity X-bone frame, supported by an independent four-wheel double-wishbone suspension setup that offers superb turn-in and communicative handling. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a fresh flush of the MTF and differential fluids. While the body exhibits some road-going patina, the mechanical components are synchronized for peak performance.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
