    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, representing a premier balance of performance and long-term value. Meticulously maintained and showing clear pride of ownership, this unit offers a refined driving experience and proven mechanical integrity. This is an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a high-caliber automobile that has been vetted for quality and roadworthiness. We invite you to experience the superior standards of our curated inventory.",
      "price": 34800.0,
