      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride, and it has been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. It runs super smooth and is ready for its next adventure! If you're looking for a quality set of wheels without the brand-new price tag, come take a look\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 33800.0,
