    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the 3.4L M97.21 flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus valve timing. The mid-ship powertrain is mated to a short-throw 6-speed manual gearbox, ensuring optimal weight distribution and a low polar moment of inertia. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec with MacPherson struts and stiffened anti-roll bars, while the braking system utilizes four-piston monoblock calipers for superior clamping force and thermal management. Recent service includes a preventive water pump replacement and a full diagnostic of the AOS (Air Oil Separator) to ensure vacuum integrity. The chassis exhibits excellent torsional rigidity, and the hydraulic steering rack provides communicative feedback. An exceptionally balanced driver\u2019s car for those who value mechanical precision and analog performance.",
